This method does not guarantee the closing of the hydrological budgets causing shifts in the global mean salinity. Global mean salinity drifts of the order of \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
